# Innere Schwarze Schneid

| first_ascent = 23 July 1874 by Theodor Petersen, Moriz von Déchy and Victor Hecht, guided by Alois Ennemoser, Johann Pinggera and Josef Spechtenhauser
| easiest_route = South ridge from Braunschweiger Hütte (UIAA-I)
}}
The Innere Schwarze Schneid is a mountain in the Weisskamm group of the Ötztal Alps.
